{"tid":1574912,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「集思廣益」完全合法不合作運動","createTime":"2019-09-16T15:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-17T16:02:40.000Z","uid":78392,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"4c408c514b179dc4f550b393ec9ac3c39966f2a9","tid":1574912,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:34:13.000Z","msg":"大家都知道今次嘅革命<br />\n一定會係長期作戰<br />\n所以我哋除咗勇武<br />\n同時都要和理非行動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">「經濟篇」</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">罷買</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=wky8n63dbjte\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fbyebuydayhk%3Figshid%3Dwky8n63dbjte&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=0fa6fa8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/byebuydayhk?igshid=wky8n63dbjte</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yB8O8Vt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyB8O8Vt.png&h=b4281caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">只支持良心小店</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/hkshoplist?igshid=1xmnaa2psu846\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fhkshoplist%3Figshid%3D1xmnaa2psu846&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=98b2abfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/hkshoplist?igshid=1xmnaa2psu846</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uGOr4ND.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuGOr4ND.png&h=b837036e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6CXhPa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6CXhPa.png&h=cd50145e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/neoguidehk?igshid=1rxeesdznq62s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fneoguidehk%3Figshid%3D1rxeesdznq62s&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbQx1bwA8BEbsE0NvOM0S0Pc%3D&h=9aca404e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/neoguidehk?igshid=1rxeesdznq62s</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k7wX2f1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk7wX2f1.png&h=097b4ea7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢2個黃藍地圖互補其短<br />\n2個都要用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都要幫手報料<br />\n只要你用過一次就會係google map儲存<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7aYMKV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7aYMKV.png&h=9fd1d28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AT6pHhn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAT6pHhn.png&h=9727e0d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和你試</span></span><br />\n大家都係有良知嘅香港人<br />\n平時可能比較少試食試用<br />\n不過要長期作戰<br />\n我哋要令到對家嘅經濟受損<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">level 1</span>經過無良商店，一定要試食試用，只用不買<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">level 2</span>自備日用品出街，例如水樽。<br />\n我就每次都會帶空水樽出街，然後去M記攞水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">level 3</span>路過無良餐廳攞多幾張籌令到食客以為要排長龍放棄。<br />\n建議攞多人數既籌，咁樣間餐廳就要hold住一張大枱<br />\n被迫同藍絲親友食無良餐廳食耐啲霸耐啲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黨鐵</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">所有學生同我用長者咭</span><br />\n<br />\n利申 和理非 唔識得勇武戰略<br />\n咩打狗救人<br />\n咩五分鐘黃金時間<br />\n咩打波組隊舉手"},{"pid":"997db5cd48abeaaa127aad885c577bc52ceeb771","tid":1574912,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T15:34:44.000Z","msg":"915國旗行動好成功!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573307\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573307</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4jR5wr1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbn